<name>STEERING</name>
<section id="1000U_S0013" variety="S0013">
<name>STEERING COLUMN</name>
<ttl id="1000U_S0013_730F7_T00F5" variety="T00F5">
<name>ELECTRIC STEERING LOCK</name>
<para id="RM000000XWL008X" category="D" type-id="3001B" name-id="SR00N-10" from="200601">
<name>HOW TO PROCEED WITH TROUBLESHOOTING</name>
<subpara id="RM000000XWL008X_z0" proc-id="RM0250U___00009ZA00000">
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>The intelligent tester can be used at steps 2, 6, 9 and 12.</ptxt>
<descript-diag>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>VEHICLE BROUGHT TO WORKSHOP</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CHECK AND CLEAR DTCS</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>PROBLEM SYMPTOM CONFIRMATION</testtitle>
<results>
<result/>
<action-ci-right>SYMPTOM DOES NOT OCCUR (Go to step 4)</action-ci-right>
<result/>
<action-ci-right>SYMPTOM OCCURS (Go to step 5)</action-ci-right>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>SYMPTOM SIMULATION</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CHECK CAN COMMUNICATION SYSTEM</testtitle>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Check that there are no problems in the CAN communication system before troubleshooting the steering lock system.</ptxt>
</atten4>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>DTC CHECK</testtitle>
<results>
<result/>
<action-ci-right>DTC IS NOT OUTPUT (Go to step 7)</action-ci-right>
<result/>
<action-ci-right>DTC IS OUTPUT (Go to step 8)</action-ci-right>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>PROBLEM SYMPTOMS TABLE</testtitle>
<results>
<result/>
<action-ci-right>Go to step 9</action-ci-right>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>DTC CHART</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CIRCUIT INSPECTION</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>PROBLEM IDENTIFICATION</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACEMENT</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CONFIRMATION TEST</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
<action-ci-fin>END</action-ci-fin>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
</descript-diag>
</content5>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
